"""Checks that all the tensors in the graph are reachable from outputs."""
graph = sess.graph
ignore_strings = ['^.*/assert_less_equal/.*$', '^.*/dilation_rate$',
    '^.*/Tensordot/concat$', '^.*/Tensordot/concat/axis$', '^testing/.*$']
ignore_regexes = [re.compile(x) for x in ignore_strings]
unreachable = self.get_unreachable_ops(graph, outputs)
filtered_unreachable = []
for x in unreachable:
    do_ignore = False
    for r in ignore_regexes:
        m = r.match(x.name)
        if m is not None:
            do_ignore = True
    if do_ignore:
        continue
    filtered_unreachable.append(x)
unreachable = filtered_unreachable
self.assertEqual(len(unreachable), 0, 
    'The following ops are unreachable: %s' % ' '.join([x.name for x in
    unreachable]))
